WHO   — The Kwisatz Haderach — the Shortening of the Way
WHAT  — The male the Bene Gesserit bred to be many places at once, whose prescience bridges space and time.
WHERE — D1 · Dune  Framework inputs: The cosmology — the messianic culmination of the Bene Gesserit breeding program  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
